# Summary
This documentation describes the Cordial destination integration with Amplitude, which enables syncing Amplitude cohorts to Cordial lists for targeted messaging and importing real-time customer data from Cordial to Amplitude for analysis, including detailed setup instructions for both platforms and the cohort syncing process.

